parameters:
\SE[4]Hey, Father? Why are you supporting this area?
\SE[0]The living standards here are low, and isn't it
difficult to collect resources?

Ah, that's an investment for the future. It doesn't have
much meaning on its own... But in about three years, we will
definitely reach a turning point. The energy structure will
evolve to the next level.

When that happens... the situation will be reversed. Now,
things that are only worth as much as pebbles will be traded
like gems.

...This is the preparation for that. In order to smoothly
proceed at that time, we are prioritizing interaction with
the local residents.

\SE[2](Master, I've been keeping it a secret, but...
\SE[3]You're predicting the soaring value of Rare Earth,
aren't you? \SE[3]...Even though it's such confidential
information, \SE[3]you're so accurate...)

\SE[37](I have something to report... My heart is torn...
I'm troubled.)

\SE[13]W-What kind of transaction is happening here!?
\SE[10]Is it because they have high expectations for the
future...?
